        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.4: \"Electron micrographs demonstrating the subcellular localization of ml receptor protein\"\n- \"J, Electron micrograph demonstrating presynaptic localization of m 1 receptor protein in an axon terminal (m) forming an asymmetrical synapse with an m 1 -immunoreactive spine (s).\"\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Twelve young adult male Sprague-Dawley (Harlan) rats were deeply anesthetized ...\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
